data.description: Discover the inviting ambiance of this charming home, nestled on over half an acre land. A covered front porch welcomes you, providing the perfect spot to enjoy the surroundings. The beautiful main level boasts an open concept design featuring a formal dining room, a living room, and a well-appointed kitchen all adorned with stylish LVP flooring, providing both elegance and durability. The kitchen, a focal point of the main level, is equipped with an island that doubles as a bar, offering a convenient space for casual meals and entertaining. The tiled backsplash adds a touch of sophistication. Venture to the lower level, where you'll find a second versatile living area with endless possibilities for entertainment and relaxation. This level also includes a bedroom and a full bath, while the upper level features two more bedrooms and a full bath. The fenced in spacious backyard is complete with a screened-in porch for year-round enjoyment and a shed for additional storage. This tri-level gem offers a perfect blend of comfort and functionality. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home.
